data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the gated and sold-out community of Waterston. This upgraded Smart Home is just over a year old and comes with all the bells and whistles. Blue Spruce boasts 5 bedrooms & 3 bathrooms, offering ample space for comfortable living & entertaining.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by natural light through the open floor plan. The well-appointed kitchen features upgraded appliances, ample cabinet space, walk in pantry, & a large island perfect for casual dining and hosting gatherings.
The oversized slider leads to an extended covered patio and a backyard with views to the San Tan Mountains.
Generously sized bedrooms provide retreats for relaxation, while the bathrooms offer both style and convenience. Not only is the home perfection, so is it's location! The home is a two minute walk to Rice Elementary School, a 3 minute walk to the beautiful community pool, the clubhouse and several parks! This prime Gilbert location cannot be beat! See attached document for a list of upgrades found throughout this beautiful home
